@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "Learn about BestPicksHub - your trusted source for honest product reviews, detailed comparisons, and expert buying guides.";
}

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-page">
            <h1>About BestPicksHub</h1>
            <p class="lead-text">Smart Choices. Honest Reviews. That's our promise.</p>

            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>BestPicksHub is a team of passionate researchers, tech enthusiasts, and consumer advocates dedicated to helping you make informed purchasing decisions. We spend hundreds of hours researching, testing, and comparing products so you don't have to.</p>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>In a world flooded with options, finding the right product can feel overwhelming. Our mission is simple: cut through the noise and deliver honest, well-researched recommendations that save you time and money.</p>

            <h2>How We Review Products</h2>
            <p>Every product review on BestPicksHub follows a rigorous process:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Research:</strong> We analyze specifications, user reviews, expert opinions, and market data.</li>
                <li><strong>Comparison:</strong> Products are evaluated against competitors in their category.</li>
                <li><strong>Rating:</strong> Each product receives an honest rating based on value, quality, features, and user experience.</li>
                <li><strong>Updates:</strong> We regularly update our reviews to reflect price changes, new models, and user feedback.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
            <p>BestPicksHub is reader-supported. When you buy through affiliate links on our site, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This never influences our reviews or recommendations. We recommend products because they're genuinely good, not because we earn from them.</p>

            <h2>Categories We Cover</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Electronics & Gadgets</li>
                <li>Software & Digital Products</li>
                <li>Health & Fitness</li>
                <li>Home & Kitchen</li>
                <li>Books & Online Courses</li>
                <li>Gaming & Entertainment</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Have questions, suggestions, or want to collaborate? We'd love to hear from you. Visit our <a href="/home/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
